{"word":"κέλης","slug":"κέλης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κέλης</b></el> <el>(κέλης, ητος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κέλλω'><el>κέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a courser, riding-horse</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a fast-sailing yacht</i> with one bank of oars, <i>a light vessel</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>celox</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}